WEBVTT

00:00:04.620 --> 00:00:07.630
<font size="15" color="#626458">Run At Full Speed</font>

00:00:04.890 --> 00:00:09.900
{\an1}Episode 13
 Galloping After Our Dreams

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:09.510
Dia-chan...

00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:12.950
McQueen-san...

00:00:12.950 --> 00:00:16.070
Excuse me? You wanna run at Arima?

00:00:16.070 --> 00:00:16.640
Yeah.

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:19.010
But even if you do... you're kinda...

00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:20.790
Your times haven't been improving.

00:00:20.790 --> 00:00:23.370
And your first race in the 
year would be in the G1.

00:00:23.370 --> 00:00:25.130
Are you sure you wanna do this?

00:00:25.130 --> 00:00:27.150
It's not about whether I want to.

00:00:27.390 --> 00:00:29.770
I'm gonna win! No matter what.

00:00:29.990 --> 00:00:31.310
You're serious, huh?

00:00:31.310 --> 00:00:31.980
Yeah.

00:00:33.940 --> 00:00:38.620
Okay. If that's what you want, it's my job 
to support you with everything I've got.

00:00:38.620 --> 00:00:42.080
More than anything else, I wanna 
see Tokai Teio running again.

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:43.450
Trainer!

00:00:43.450 --> 00:00:44.830
Teio-san!

00:00:44.830 --> 00:00:47.710
If there's anything we can 
do to help, let us know!

00:00:47.710 --> 00:00:51.630
As the team's second leader, I can 
lend you as many hands as I've got.

00:00:51.630 --> 00:00:53.090
We owe you plenty, after all.

00:00:53.090 --> 00:00:54.420
That's true.

00:00:57.870 --> 00:00:59.530
Thanks, guys!

00:01:00.050 --> 00:01:01.860
I'm gonna do my best.

00:01:08.690 --> 00:01:11.230
Hey, looks like 1st place in the fan vote...

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:12.730
Arima Kinen Fan Vote Final Results!

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:12.730
Which Horse Girl Will Take the Last GI Race of the Year?!

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:12.730
Biwa Hayahide

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:12.730
Winning Ticket

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:12.960
went to Biwa Hayahide, after all.

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.260
Of course it did.

00:01:14.260 --> 00:01:17.270
She's never placed lower than second... 
and she dominated at the Kikkashou.

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:16.280
Arima Kinen Fan Vote Results Announced

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:16.280
Arima Kinen Fan Vote Results Announced

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:16.280
Arima Kinen Fan Vote Results Announced

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:16.280
Arima Kinen Fan Vote Results Announced

00:01:17.270 --> 00:01:20.070
Winning Ticket and Rice Shower were picked, too.

00:01:20.070 --> 00:01:21.780
This is going to be one hell of a lineup!

00:01:21.780 --> 00:01:24.020
Hey, Tokai Teio made fourth place!

00:01:24.020 --> 00:01:26.210
Oh, then Teio's going to run at Arima?!

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:26.820
Teio!

00:01:26.820 --> 00:01:30.320
Getting 4th place in a fan ranking 
after not running for a whole year...

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:33.010
Tokai Teio is seriously popular.

00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:33.750
Teio's

00:01:33.430 --> 00:01:35.610
I can't wait to see her race again.

00:01:35.610 --> 00:01:37.460
Well, even if she runs, her odds are rough.

00:01:37.460 --> 00:01:39.270
It's been a whole year since she last raced,

00:01:39.270 --> 00:01:42.140
and she's up against seven 
other G1 horse girls...

00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:42.510
Arima Kinen Fan Vote Results Announced

00:01:42.140 --> 00:01:44.520
Not to mention no horse girl has ever won

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:48.190
their first race after coming 
off such a long hiatus.

00:01:50.020 --> 00:01:51.020
Here you are!

